	    						“Insurer” means:
	    						<ol style="list-style-type: lower-alpha; margin:0; margin-left: 13px;">
	    							<li>Industrial Alliance Pacific Insurance and Financial Services Inc. for all Certificates with the Effective Date prior to July 1, 2012; or</li>
	    							<li>Industrial Alliance Insurance and Financial Services Inc. for all Certificates with the Effective Date on or after July 1, 2012.</li>
