	    				<div class="small-top-gap form-medium-text bolder">SECTION 6 – DISABILITY INSURANCE - ACCIDENTAL PLUS</div>
	    				<div class="form-small-text bolder underliner">Accidental Plus Disability Insurance includes two types of coverage:</div>
